    <div class="col-xs-12 debate-date">
        <strong>29 May 1951</strong>
    </div>

    <div class="col-xs-12 debate-date">Volume 488</div>

    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
        <div class="container">
            <div id="debateContent">
                <div class="highlightedSearchTerms"></div>
                <div class="content-container">
<div class="content-item" id="contribution-bc0cf3b8-82f6-4263-b1f1-b52e8bc198e2">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-bc0cf3b8-82f6-4263-b1f1-b52e8bc198e2">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-bc0cf3b8-82f6-4263-b1f1-b52e8bc198e2">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-bc0cf3b8-82f6-4263-b1f1-b52e8bc198e2">
                Major Sir David Maxwell Fyfe
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-bc0cf3b8-82f6-4263-b1f1-b52e8bc198e2" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-05-29/debates/23c31842-800c-4b92-8561-acfb8a2e6f26/RoadHaulageStrike#contribution-bc0cf3b8-82f6-4263-b1f1-b52e8bc198e2">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">(<em>by Private Notice</em>) asked the Minister of Labour whether he has any statement to make on the strike taking place in the nationalised road transport industry?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-bc0cf3b8-82f6-4263-b1f1-b52e8bc198e2" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-05-29/debates/23c31842-800c-4b92-8561-acfb8a2e6f26/RoadHaulageStrike#contribution-bc0cf3b8-82f6-4263-b1f1-b52e8bc198e2">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-cfd586e8-c939-4327-9966-716e11e70229">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-cfd586e8-c939-4327-9966-716e11e70229">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-cfd586e8-c939-4327-9966-716e11e70229">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-cfd586e8-c939-4327-9966-716e11e70229">
                The Minister of Labour (Mr. Robens)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-cfd586e8-c939-4327-9966-716e11e70229" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-05-29/debates/23c31842-800c-4b92-8561-acfb8a2e6f26/RoadHaulageStrike#contribution-cfd586e8-c939-4327-9966-716e11e70229">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Out of a total of some 41,000 drivers, 11,635 were not at work this morning. This stoppage has arisen over a decision by the Road Haulage Executive to extend the system of road patrols of which a limited number are at present employed. This decision was taken only after long and careful consideration and after full consultation with the Staff Council. I understand there is some apprehension amongst the men that these patrols will be used to spy on them, but the Road Haulage Executive inform me that the men will be in uniform and will travel in distinctive vans. The arrangements can have no immediate application as no appointments have yet been made.<p></p> In all the circumstances I have today-invited representatives of the Executive and of the trade union to meet me to discuss the matter.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-cfd586e8-c939-4327-9966-716e11e70229" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-05-29/debates/23c31842-800c-4b92-8561-acfb8a2e6f26/RoadHaulageStrike#contribution-cfd586e8-c939-4327-9966-716e11e70229">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-e5c5c5b6-a3fe-4f09-8c50-4099edbd8952">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-e5c5c5b6-a3fe-4f09-8c50-4099edbd8952">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-e5c5c5b6-a3fe-4f09-8c50-4099edbd8952">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-e5c5c5b6-a3fe-4f09-8c50-4099edbd8952">
                Sir D. Maxwell Fyfe
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-e5c5c5b6-a3fe-4f09-8c50-4099edbd8952" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-05-29/debates/23c31842-800c-4b92-8561-acfb8a2e6f26/RoadHaulageStrike#contribution-e5c5c5b6-a3fe-4f09-8c50-4099edbd8952">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Can the right hon. Gentleman help us on two points? First, what is the position, particularly in the London area, with regard to milk, perishable goods and hospital supplies? Secondly—a different point, but one which he will notice has been the subject of much comment—has he any information whether the drivers on strike were consulted before the agreement was made on this point?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-e5c5c5b6-a3fe-4f09-8c50-4099edbd8952" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-05-29/debates/23c31842-800c-4b92-8561-acfb8a2e6f26/RoadHaulageStrike#contribution-e5c5c5b6-a3fe-4f09-8c50-4099edbd8952">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-2f9e1c5d-2c9c-41e6-92e5-ccf587335711">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-2f9e1c5d-2c9c-41e6-92e5-ccf587335711">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-2f9e1c5d-2c9c-41e6-92e5-ccf587335711">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-2f9e1c5d-2c9c-41e6-92e5-ccf587335711">
                Mr. Robens
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-2f9e1c5d-2c9c-41e6-92e5-ccf587335711" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-05-29/debates/23c31842-800c-4b92-8561-acfb8a2e6f26/RoadHaulageStrike#contribution-2f9e1c5d-2c9c-41e6-92e5-ccf587335711">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">As to the first question, there is at the moment no danger to those essential supplies, but we are watching that position very closely indeed. As to the second question, I would rather wait until I have met the representatives of the trade union and of the Executive.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-2f9e1c5d-2c9c-41e6-92e5-ccf587335711" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-05-29/debates/23c31842-800c-4b92-8561-acfb8a2e6f26/RoadHaulageStrike#contribution-2f9e1c5d-2c9c-41e6-92e5-ccf587335711">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





