    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-46215f23-fdc3-43f6-9315-5818309df1e5">
                Mr. Peter Thorneycroft
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-46215f23-fdc3-43f6-9315-5818309df1e5" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-05-29/debates/23c31842-800c-4b92-8561-acfb8a2e6f26/RoadHaulageStrike#contribution-46215f23-fdc3-43f6-9315-5818309df1e5">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Has the right hon. Gentleman's attention been called to the efforts which the Minister of Transport is stated to be making to enable the private road haulage industry to keep the <span id="38" class="column-number" data-column-number="38"></span> essential traffics running by lifting the 25-mile ban? Can he say to what extent this ban has been lifted in the emergency and how successful that operation has been?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-46215f23-fdc3-43f6-9315-5818309df1e5" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-05-29/debates/23c31842-800c-4b92-8561-acfb8a2e6f26/RoadHaulageStrike#contribution-46215f23-fdc3-43f6-9315-5818309df1e5">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





